{"data":{"conclusion":{"html":"<p>测试方面的现状则稍显不同。如今，JavaScript 生态系统的其他部分在经过一段时间的发展与沉淀后日渐稳定，且已产生几个公认的解决方案。相比之下，测试方面则还处在混乱时期：许多不同的或相互配合的工具相对平均地瓜分了测试工具体系。尽管如此，开发者对测试环境的解决方案整体上还是满意的。根据今年的调查结果，测试类工具满意度最低的也有 68%。</p>\n<p>调查结果还显示，<strong>Mocha</strong> 依旧是当下最热门的单元测试框架，它坐拥超过一万名用户。由于 Mocha 的存在时间较长，因此它拥有测试框架中最大的生态系统，而且大部分 Node.js 开发者也很熟悉它。</p>\n<p><strong>Jest</strong> 在使用量方面仅次于 Mocha；但相对于 Mocha 82% 的满意度，Jest 的满意度为 96%。值得注意的是，Jest 96% 的满意度，在今年调查的所有工具中排名第二，第一名是 ES6。</p>\n<p>看来，开发者对 Facebook 提供的这个功能完备的测试框架十分满意。Jest 一开始只是用来测试 React 组件的，但现在它不光可以用来测试前端代码，甚至可以用于测试后端代码。而这一切都不需要进行额外地配置。</p>\n<p>在“单页面应用”时代，随着越来越多的逻辑被迁移到客户端，网页应用已经变得越来越复杂。今年的调查也表明，开发者会使用多种测试类工具来测试他们开发的应用。</p>\n<p>其实，测试包含很多方面：单元测试、集成测试、端对端测试，同时还有“视觉测试”（visual testing）。值得注意的是 <strong>Storybook</strong>，它是“视觉测试”方面一个很好的应用，同时也是这类工具中满意度第二高的。</p>\n<p>测试的其中一个未来趋势就是在浏览器中引入自动化测试。我们会考虑在下一年的调查中添加此类工具，比如 <a href=\"https://www.cypress.io/\">Cypress</a>。同时，我们应该会在明年看到更多基于 <a href=\"https://pptr.dev/\">Puppeteer</a> 的新工具。</p>"},"opinions":{"opinions":[{"survey_id":"2016","tools":[{"tool_id":"mocha","counts":{"would_use":4665,"would_not_use":308,"interested":3071,"not_interested":1053,"never_heard":1153}},{"tool_id":"jasmine","counts":{"would_use":4078,"would_not_use":815,"interested":2820,"not_interested":1302,"never_heard":1235}},{"tool_id":"jest","counts":{"would_use":482,"would_not_use":338,"interested":1701,"not_interested":1184,"never_heard":6545}},{"tool_id":"enzyme","counts":{"would_use":1075,"would_not_use":58,"interested":1405,"not_interested":604,"never_heard":7108}},{"tool_id":"ava","counts":{"would_use":386,"would_not_use":66,"interested":995,"not_interested":573,"never_heard":8230}}]},{"survey_id":"2017","tools":[{"tool_id":"mocha","counts":{"would_use":10694,"would_not_use":1551,"interested":6585,"not_interested":2582,"never_heard":2254}},{"tool_id":"jasmine","counts":{"would_use":9214,"would_not_use":2361,"interested":5769,"not_interested":3289,"never_heard":3033}},{"tool_id":"jest","counts":{"would_use":5845,"would_not_use":396,"interested":6455,"not_interested":1964,"never_heard":9006}},{"tool_id":"enzyme","counts":{"would_use":4567,"would_not_use":268,"interested":3392,"not_interested":1913,"never_heard":13526}},{"tool_id":"ava","counts":{"would_use":1174,"would_not_use":391,"interested":2175,"not_interested":1922,"never_heard":18004}}]},{"survey_id":"2018","tools":[{"tool_id":"storybook","counts":{"would_use":3085,"would_not_use":379,"interested":4767,"not_interested":1225,"never_heard":10547}},{"tool_id":"mocha","counts":{"would_use":7873,"would_not_use":1683,"interested":5238,"not_interested":3133,"never_heard":2022}},{"tool_id":"jasmine","counts":{"would_use":5689,"would_not_use":1919,"interested":4971,"not_interested":4515,"never_heard":2843}},{"tool_id":"jest","counts":{"would_use":7910,"would_not_use":289,"interested":5923,"not_interested":1783,"never_heard":4047}},{"tool_id":"enzyme","counts":{"would_use":4039,"would_not_use":528,"interested":3612,"not_interested":2455,"never_heard":9289}},{"tool_id":"ava","counts":{"would_use":804,"would_not_use":320,"interested":1734,"not_interested":2674,"never_heard":14419}},{"tool_id":"karma","counts":{"would_use":3676,"would_not_use":1744,"interested":3788,"not_interested":4091,"never_heard":6633}}]}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"conclusion","type":"conclusion","section":"testing","previous":{"id":"other-libraries","type":"other-libraries","section":"testing","basePath":"/testing/other-libraries/"},"next":{"id":"mobile-and-desktop","type":"section","basePath":"/mobile-and-desktop/overview/"},"basePath":"/testing/conclusion/","locale":"zh-CN","localeLabel":"简体中文","localePath":"/cn"}}